{"tid":101593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逃票被老虎咬死　家屬要園方負責：不能給人翻進去的機會","createTime":"2017-01-31T03:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T06:54:56.000Z","uid":32051,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca1c2de8904981888a90f39947dca79cde0122a8","tid":101593,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:49:52.000Z","msg":"浙江寧波一名張姓男子29日為了逃票，翻牆進入雅戈爾動物園，沒想到誤入老虎區，當場被群虎圍攻而死，老虎也在警方救人的過程中被槍殺。今日死者已被帶往山上依家鄉風俗下葬，但他的親戚卻認為園方有疏失，「動物園管理不當，他不能給人翻進去的機會呀，所以要負責任！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/31/114610_a2371a6c3f67f409f7cd46221ab0c88c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F31%2F114610_a2371a6c3f67f409f7cd46221ab0c88c.jpg&h=4cc91f14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲男子送醫後不治。（圖／翻攝微博，下同。）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2307/d2307288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2307%2Fd2307288.jpg&h=e4ccf51f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n動物園的管理委員會表示，張姓男子當天帶著妻子、兩個孩子和友人一起來動物園，妻子和孩子都有購票入場，但張男和同行友人為了逃票，竟從後方潛入，「他們無視警告標誌，先鑽過一層鐵絲網，然後又翻過一層3公尺高的圍牆，張男先進入老虎區，馬上就被好幾隻老虎圍攻。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據《梨視頻》報導，張姓男子的親戚楊先生表示，男子是基層打工者，一個月只賺幾千元人民幣，上有父母、下有兩小兒，家境困難，動物園一定要負責任，「就算他是為了逃票從後面翻牆進去的，那也是動物園管理不當，<span style=\"color: red;\">不能給別人翻進去的機會，你既然有漏洞，別人就會想鑽漏洞呀，所以動物園有責任!</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170130/858512.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170130%2F858512.htm&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=481f7c29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170130/858512.htm</a>"},{"pid":"920de9df6993a64e31adcaebf64ad47cf5c96d14","tid":101593,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:50:49.000Z","msg":"老虎rip"},{"pid":"c86a65382c7912187b0c61289839dbcaa87c2c40","tid":101593,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:52:25.000Z","msg":"佢自己唔夠老虎打姐"},{"pid":"d147a8171fad44cfa6ee059cc8c693ecd0afde05","tid":101593,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:53:28.000Z","msg":"弱智係佢父母嘅責任"},{"pid":"06a4ad878a789c90d753f44a31f3a255b4f6b2f5","tid":101593,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:54:20.000Z","msg":"個老豆已經得到應得既報應"},{"pid":"3fa80b1152c1628d37092a7aca10ff85287783b2","tid":101593,"uid":10699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"隔離post 呢單新聞果陣有班人話家屬一定屈間動物園負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e92a0b5a5ac1d087c5b27be6d8c1ce73891f7e5","tid":101593,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:56:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隔離post 呢單新聞果陣有班人話家屬一定屈間動物園負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為次次都會<br />\n今次唔會就奇怪"},{"pid":"281070207410a15b4f0cb708516305c8f76c4277","tid":101593,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:57:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁點解班蝗又從來唔敢屌&quot;不應有讓人翻牆&quot;呢仆街？？？？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a506a40e5c56be2043cb331c567d74d10a19695b","tid":101593,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:00:49.000Z","msg":"喺到搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413472ed71149f30c94e0b7b8f993b6b7f4e4fb9","tid":101593,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:03:48.000Z","msg":"錯就要認 要對方認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0480c0407e9df382984eb5fbc626637ac663335d","tid":101593,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017